---
title: Sweet Soy Chicken & Yam Nourish Bowl with Celery Slaw & Parsley
description: If yams are on the menu then fire up that oven and get ready for a delicious dinner. Sweet and soy chicken in a rich sauce will be the perfect accompaniment to the vibrant veggies. If yams weren’t enough to quip your interest, there’s even a sprinkling of sesame seeds in the mix.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
